nt  We follow careful cleaning procedures throughout Post  Athletic department and physical education staff are educated about the infection and watch their students carefully  The Infirmary nurses and doctors have extensive experience with diagnosing and treating the infection  We follow Center for Disease Control guidelines and monitor changes in recommendations  Read more about MRSA  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 